Description:
Soak up the Sun in a Lifestyle Locale
Leave the bustle behind and elevate your view on life thanks to this sun-splashed top floor apartment. Simply steps to the station, cafes and shops, this is a home where you have the ideal combination of peaceful interiors yet a location with everything on your doorstep.
Set up high on the north-west corner of the block, this sleek abode is embraced on two sides by an oversized wraparound terrace that captures far-reaching views and streams of sun throughout the day right until dusk.
Inside, the large living and dining zone has been refreshed with new floors and crisp paint, the stone kitchen with stainless steel appliances also boasting modernised cabinetry.
Offering space for a study or reading nook if desired, the master bedroom boasts a walk thru robe to a glossy en-suite, whilst the second bedroom is a true double and offers a mirrored robe. Servicing the home is a spacious main bathroom with stone vanity and hidden euro laundry, whilst wrapping up the package are ducted heating/cooling, video intercom entry plus two parking spaces and storage cage.
Step out and enjoy a premium lifestyle in this prized McKinnon Secondary College zoned neighbourhood.
Insights: 14/498 North Road, Ormond VIC 3204 was last sold in 2019 and 49 other 2 bedroom unit in Ormond have recently been sold.

Description:
Where design & lifestyle converge
Boasting a contemporary urban design & world-class craftsmanship, this sun-filled apartment presents a rewarding opportunity for those seeking a central lifestyle. Part of a boutique complex & situated on the first floor, it boasts on-trend wide oak flooring in the open-plan domain that flaunts a stunning Smeg kitchen with stone island bench, mirrored splashback & custom soft touch joinery. Sliding doors take you outside to a full-length balcony that presents the ultimate setting for a coffee & the weekend paper. Two spacious carpeted bedrooms both have mirrored built-ins - one is complemented by a designer bathroom with decadent shower. A second bathroom with quality finishes adds further appeal, as does the Euro laundry. This urban gem also boasts intercom entry, lift access & a stacker carpark & separate storage cage on title. Located amidst cosmopolitan surrounds, it is walking distance to Ormond retail & dining precinct, Ormond train station & all the nearby amenities of this buzzing locale.

Description:
Stylish townhouse, Village convenience
Elegantly updated proportions enjoy the privacy and independence of a street front position in this impeccable modern townhouse just metres from Ormond Village. Behind its own secure garden entry and driveway, generous four-bedroom two-bathroom accommodation provides the perfect balance of style, space and low maintenance ease with cafes, eateries, trains and schools available within a short stroll. Elevated ceilings and timber floors frame bright open plan living/dining areas that flow to a sun filled northern courtyard where a night lit undercover deck provides year-round entertaining with strip heating and overhead fan. A downstairs bedroom with BIR complements three upstairs bedrooms, all with WIRs and air conditioners, the beautiful main featuring a lavish designer ensuite with soaker bath and walk in shower. An upstairs study/sitting retreat adds further flexibility alongside a second bathroom, dedicated laundry and a classic contemporary kitchen featuring stone benchtops, stainless steel appliances and excellent storage. Features powder room, split system heating/cooling throughout, alarm system, video intercom security, plenty of natural light and blue sky outlooks, internally accessed remote double garage and remote gated OSP.

Description:
A Prime McKinnon Zone Proposition
Be amazed at the deep level west-facing lawn that's kept secret behind this traditional 70s 3 bedroom brick home. An exceptional 699sqm approx. in the prized McKinnon Secondary College zone, this sought after property makes an excellent investment property, beautifully cared for by the current tenants. In authentic original order, this cheery charmer features a casual living area, funky orange/timber kitchen/meals, 3 double bedrooms (BIRs), an immaculate original bathroom, separate toilet and laundry. With so much scope to renovate this mid-century marvel, rebuild or redevelop (STCA), this time-honoured property is appointed with gas heating, air conditioning and parking for 2. Opposite the beautiful Joyce Park, a heartbeat to McKinnon Secondary College, North Road shops and restaurants, and the train, zoned for McKinnon Primary School.

Small group, big benefits, high amenity location!
Move in and relax, rent out and be rewarded, secure your place in this small group in a high amenity location. Just 100m from the heart of the Ormond retail and rail strip, easy walk to schools & parklands, this charming two bedroom villa is big on comforts with a plush carpeted lounge extending to tiled dining beside glossy stone and European appliance kitchen and robe fitted bedrooms serviced by a fresh white bathroom with a handy separate WC.
Optioned up with ducted heating and multiple air conditioners, this quality home has ceiling fans for both bedroom and full size laundry. With a private courtyard wrapping around to access an auto entry garage, this inviting unit even has a bonus covered entry patio catching north sun out front!
Find the shops at the door, the station within two blocks and the bus to Chadstone at the end of the streetthen enjoy the big benefits of this small group in this wonderfully well-presented home!

Classic Deco Warmth in College Zone
Absolutely immaculate, this charming 3 bedroom Art Deco treasure sits on 663sqm approx. of prime McKinnon Secondary College zoned land, creating a unique opportunity to cosmetically update the existing home, extend, rebuild or redevelop (STCA). Invitingly spacious, this family classic features a security porch, a wide foyer, 3 good size bedrooms (BIRs), double glass doors into the delightful lounge (potential fireplace), adjoining dining room (potential fireplace), double doors to the huge American Oak kitchen overlooking the timber lined north facing meals area and casual family room, central spa bathroom, 2nd bathroom and large laundry. Description:
Period-Prestige in a Prime Position
Discreetly extended, prestige appointed and positioned in the coveted McKinnon Secondary College Zone, this beautiful family home offers period beauty, modern amenity and a location to last a lifetime.
A superior example of Californian Bungalow with lovely period detail as a backdrop to contemporary design, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home enjoys open plan living and dining around a prestige stainless steel appliance kitchen, dual vanity ensuite bathrooms (one with clever two-way access) and a large master domain with generous walk-in robes.
Presented in timeless style with stone benchtops, timber floors, plantation shutters and detailed cornices for the high ceilings, this family showpiece provides a bonus powder room, ducted heating/cooling, alarm and great off street parking.
But its the entertaining outdoors that families will love. With something for everyone, theres a fan-cooled deck for al fresco entertaining, great lawn space for the kids and a cubby house to play all set in deep 708sqm approx gardens.
On a prized street of prestige and period homes, this timeless home has Allnutt Park within seconds, schools within minutes and Centre Rd restaurant, rail and retail precinct within easy reach.

Expressions of Interest Closing Tuesday 29th October at 5pm
Californian Class on a Grand Scale
Sitting pretty in lush green gardens accentuating the classical beauty of the home, this exquisite 5 bedroom + study 2.5 bathroom Californian Bungalow has been transformed into a spectacular entertainer. Retaining its original façade with its leadlights and decorative glass doors, this magnificent home enjoys a wide hallway with Red Mahogany floors, a gorgeous sitting room with open fireplace, adjoining north facing dining room, beautiful downstairs main bedroom suite (2 sided WIR & a porcelain tiled ensuite), large study with picture window overlooking the central paved courtyard; a fitted laundry and powder room. Indoor outdoor entertaining comes to the fore in the amazing open plan entertaining area with its stone gas fireplace, 2 sets of bi-fold doors leading onto the sun drenched covered deck with BBQ kitchen and the sublime stone/marble kitchen with its 900mm Blanco stove and huge walk in pantry. Upstairs is designed for the family with its 4 big bedrooms (WIRs), a stylish living area and sparkling bathroom. The low maintenance rear garden has honed bluestone paving, lush lawn and espaliered pear trees to complement the outdoor living. Architect designed to give contemporary living period class, this superb family home is appointed with ducted R/C air conditioning, an alarm, high ceilings, ducted vacuum, instant hot water with temperature control, exceptional storage and auto gates to a carport and a double auto garage beyond. In the coveted McKinnon Secondary College and McKinnon Primary School zones, a heartbeat to Joyce Park, North Road shops and restaurants, Monash University bus and Ormond station.

Description:
In Zone & Out Front Family Prestige
Front up to Gold Star family living in the Zone! Architectural, adaptable and in the Zone, this family-sized three bedroom plus study area, 2.5 bathroom streetfront home from in-demand Knight Building Group puts you out in front in versatile style! Showcasing state-of-the-art style with airy open-plan living around a streamlined elite appliance kitchen (with integrated Hafele fridge), this flexible family design features a vast master suite (with bespoke-fitted walk-in-robe and deluxe dual vanity ensuite) and a second living zone on the first-floor - easily transformed as a sizeable third bedroom.
Designed to adapt to every size and shape of family with a clever treetop study area, basement garaging and storage, and a super-sized lawned and decked walled courtyard, this outstanding home stands out with this leading builder's signature style. In this fine design, cool stone benchtops meet subway-tile splashbacks, concrete-look and feature tiles wrap both bathrooms, and designer finishes include wideboard Oak floors and plush charcoal carpets, the latest bold black tapware and hardware, and a striking 'glass-box' pillarless corner-window.
Climate-controlled by a Daikin reverse-cycle system, this is sensational streetfront home has the security of video-intercom, the ease of lift-access to the garage and the entertaining edge of BBQ plumbing for the entertainers' deck. Best of all, it has this flagship streetfront position this family-wise locale; just steps from the shopping, cafes and restaurants of the North Rd retail and rail strip, one block to the fresh new station, and well In-Zone for sought-after McKinnon Secondary College.

Description:
Modern Family Pride on a Single Level
Luxuriously spacious on a single level, this quality built 4 bedroom + study 2.5 bathroom entertainer caters for all your family needs. In the prestige McKinnon Secondary College zone, this beautiful home enjoys a wide tiled entry hall, double doors to a superb main bedroom (WIR & radiant ensuite), north facing lounge, an executive study/5th bedroom, impressive stone kitchen with 900mm stove and large pantry overlooking the expansive living & dining area; 3 further large bedrooms (BIRs), stylish bathroom, separate toilet and a fitted laundry. Double sliding doors open to a covered deck and a mini football-field of level lawn capturing the afternoon sun. Feeling like you've escaped to Queensland with its resort-style feel, this 'as new' haven is appointed with ducted heating, evaporative cooling, an alarm, timber blinds and a large double auto garage. Metres to McKinnon Primary School and the Secondary College, walk to North Road cafes, buses to Monash University and Ormond station and the beautiful Joyce Park.

Description:
Period Family Warmth in McKinnon Zone
Feel warm and cosy in this heartwarming 3 bedroom + study 2.5 bathroom timber period home on a single level. Welcomed by a full length decked laced verandah, this homely charmer features a delightful main bedroom with WIR & modern period style ensuite; 2 further double bedrooms (BIRs & OFP), neat bathroom, bi-fold doors to an engaging dining room (OFP & Karri pine floors), modern timber/granite kitchen with original oven hearth (Kleenmaid 900mm stove, Siemens dishwasher), a relaxed conservatory style living area with gas log fireplace and Bose entertainment system, private study/4th bedroom, tessellated tiled powder room and laundry. A covered alfresco deck acts as another living space adjoining the salt-water pool in a tropical landscape. Retaining its original polished boards, French windows, picture rails, 3 open original fireplaces and high ceilings, this casual treasure is appointed with security doors, ducted heating, 2 air conditioners, ducted vacuum, auto gate to a carport, with 2nd auto gates to a long drive with a carport/alfresco area and 2 sheds. In the McKinnon Secondary College zone, a heartbeat to North Road and Bentleigh shops, Monash University, Chadstone & Southland Shopping Centres bus and, Ormond train station, walk to Joyce Park and a choice of private and public schools.

Description:
Sun-filled single level living
This delightful single level villa presents the ultimate opportunity for first home buyers, savvy investors or downsizers seeking superior functionality, a clever floorplan & convenient locale. Blessed with the sunniest of dispositions, this easy-care home features a spacious living & dining room with leafy outdoor vistas that flow through to a kitchen & meals area where abundant storage, quality appliances & a u-shaped bench makes it the ideal setting for casual entertaining. This is made even more alluring by the adjoining courtyard that is brimming with greenery & low maintenance paving. Tucked away for supreme privacy are two carpeted bedrooms, one with walk in robe & the other with substantial built ins that share a family bathroom with a shower, bath & a separate toilet. A sizeable laundry adds greater appeal. Further benefits include ducted gas heating, split system heating/cooling, a deep lock up garage & a grassy front yard on title. Complete with enormous lifestyle benefits you can stroll down to the park, grab a coffee at a local café or take the train to the city the options are endless.
